{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "終將重逢", "storyInfo": "莫伊拉提出尋找逃生方法的計劃；米蘭妮為謝幕戲找蒂比設計場景；格蕾塔找到盧西恩，在結局未定的情況下希望他成為新的男主角，與此同時，陷入創作困境之中的斯蒂芬聽到了敲門聲……\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g6_proproom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老道爾頓的死和謝莉小姐走入冷凍庫都不是意外……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，邁克爾先生和瑪麗昂小姐也死了，還是死於那樣的場景和手段……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幕後的兇手到底是誰？為什麼要犯下這麼多樁命案？為什麼……如此殘忍？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾先生似乎早有預感。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遇害的前一天晚上他來找我的時候，神情比前幾次見面還嚴肅。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他一定是確定了道爾頓的意外背後真正的原因，才心驚膽戰想逃離這裡，但……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論他是不是心裡有鬼，我們都沒辦法知道了……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能最近發生的所有事都與他們口中說的那起五年前的意外有關，但我更擔心的是……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兇手不再將謀殺掩蓋為意外，而是將自己的存在公之於眾，他難道是想告訴我們——", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在真相徹底被揭發之前，任何人都不安全。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊對不起，莫麗，我的話是不是嚇到你了？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擔心，無論地塊上是不是遊蕩著窮兇極惡的殺手，無論對方有多少人，我都會保護你的。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，蒂比大偵探，我只是在想……我也可以做些什麼。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾先生已經遇難，但他之前拜託我的事情，不一定要作廢。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士曾提到的逃生艙或許已經被兇手盯上……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果真的能另開闢一條逃生通道，或者製造出某種連接地面的裝置，又或者哪怕只是找到一個可以讓我們通過的排風口……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定我們真的能避開那個在陰影裡盯著我們的兇手，在關鍵時刻保護自己。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，我來到這個劇組後，你是第一個跟我說話、第一個真心對待我的人。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我搞砸過很多事，也給你添過麻煩，但你凡事都擋在我的前面，哪怕瑪麗昂只是一時忘記我的名字，你也會鄭重地提醒。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一直在關心我、安慰我、保護我……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，我也想保護你。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 6.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黎博利女孩輕輕抱住她在劇組裡最最要好的朋友。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等這些事情結束之後，我們到你家去看電影……二十四小時恐怖片連播，搭配我們最喜歡的飲料和炸鱗塊。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想看看你從小長大的地方，也想看看你溫柔的姐姐究竟是什麼樣子。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我似乎打擾了你們溫馨的姐妹談心。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮女士，您怎麼會親自來道具間？您的助理呢？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們沒收到格蕾塔的終端通訊嗎？她清點並發放所有人的酬勞，正式解散了整個劇組。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畏懼兇手的、忌憚天災的、堅持拍攝的……都可以任意決定自己的去留，各行其是。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眨眼的功夫，我手下那個軟骨頭就不知道跑去哪裡躲起來了。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各行其是？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有那麼多人遇害了……難道格蕾塔女士，不，劇組的其他人都不在意這背後深層的原因是什麼嗎？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深層原因？在這種情況下難道還有人想要追尋真相嗎？直接逃離移動地塊去報警不是更方便嗎？", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者，按照格蕾塔的說法——把真相交給想當偵探的好事者吧。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您來找我們又是為了什麼？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是你們，是你，布景噴畫師蒂比。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我欣賞格蕾塔想要拍攝天災的膽識，她的鋌而走險對我個人來說也是極佳的機遇，但戲不是光靠天然的背景就能撐起來的。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，我知道你對電影的熱情遠超劇組裡的大多數成員，你也多少聽說過這部戲對我有多麼重要……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我真誠地請求你發揮在氣氛營造和色彩搭配上的天賦，為我的謝幕戲設計最完美的場景。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是很願意啦，但……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比，你去幫米蘭妮女士的忙吧。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？莫麗，你穿上雨衣是要……你真的打算去，“探險”啊？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我在道具組也待了這麼久，也算熟悉這個地塊，不會出什麼事的。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還記得我們剛剛說過的話嗎？這是我必須要去做的事情。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那好吧。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我幫完米蘭妮女士，就去找你！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g10_dormitory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請進，格蕾塔女士。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒開門就知道是我了？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我在等你。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天你暗地裡調查出的小線索，讓我不得不提前向所有成員解釋拍攝實景天災的規劃。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是個好時機。阿布納，還有劇組的其他人本就對我不滿，我只能臨時做出一些不小的決定。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果要認真計較，我甚至能以侵佔他人財物罪將你告上法庭，盧西恩。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是我不會只為了樹立威信或是宣洩情緒懲罰我的員工，當時追究你的過錯毫無意義。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之後劇組又發生了命案，兇手甚至不再掩飾自己的暴行。大家驚慌失措，你卻還像往常一樣，遠離人群冷靜旁觀。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這樣的危機之中我才終於確認，你來這裡另有目的。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，這些都已經不重要了。劇組已經解散，無論你打算離開，還是留到合約結束，隨你心意。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的戲份已經結束了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士，此刻你來找我，恰好證明我的戲份還沒結束。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我沒辦法臨時變出另一個“杜邦夫人”，也沒辦法讓三個“洛克菲勒”死而復生。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間和人手都已經所剩無幾，我必須在有限的資源下找出最好的解法。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩先生，接下來，我想讓你來擔任主角。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g13_directorstudio", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_typewriter"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深夜的辦公室，粗暴的打字聲迴響著。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_burnpaper"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滿臉頹喪的佩洛男子蜷縮在打字機前，他掃了一眼最新的那張劇稿，將菸頭按了上去。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結局、結局、結局……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杜邦夫人應該在結局死去……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“她跟第二個洛克菲勒私奔後，兩人斷絕了所有與外界的聯絡，棲居在鄉野過著詩意的生活。”", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“然而貴族生活在洛克菲勒身上遺留的痕跡太重，他羞辱了杜邦夫人虛假的姓氏後離開了她，杜邦夫人在絕望中自刎……”", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太寫實……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開奢靡生活後一定要受罰？", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是哥倫比亞歷史中最重視財富為美德的時代啊！我要的是還原它，讓觀眾評價它，而不是自己在電影中批判它！", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#5$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rollpaper"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菸頭燙出的傷痕吞沒了整張劇稿，斯蒂芬用力將灰燼吹走。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“杜邦夫人最終沒有選擇任何一個洛克菲勒，她本就想藉戀人的名義逃脫虛假的命運，卻低估了愛情的毒性。”", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“洛克菲勒兄弟不約而同策劃了三種復仇方式，最終杜邦夫人被三人同時殺死……”", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太庸俗……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不做選擇依舊陷入愛情的泥沼，看似是某種因果和宿命，實際上只是牽強附會。", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後杜邦夫人屍骨無存的畫面，確實具有一定的震撼力，但情節也太粗糙……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“杜邦夫人的家族冒充維多利亞貴族的真相最終還是暴露在公眾之前，無論三位洛克菲勒的愛有多深，他們都無法保護她免於制裁。”", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“杜邦夫人的人生中唯一一次真正享受貴族待遇的時刻，是真正的杜邦家族為她施加死刑之時……”", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太……工整！", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "精心編排，尋求表意，最後恰恰缺乏《杜邦夫人之死》裡該有的瘋狂和浪漫……！", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#5$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，怎麼稿紙又沒了，還得去文件櫃裡面拿……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,-60", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯蒂芬踩到被他丟在地上的紙團，摔個四腳朝天。"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這時他才意識到這間辦公室已經被他廢棄的劇稿淹沒，無處下腳。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他躺在枯竭的靈感中央，雙手摀住臉，崩潰大吼。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯蒂芬·奎你*藍卡塢片場術語*清醒一點！整整兩個月你都在修改結局，到現在連一個勉強能用的橋段都沒有！", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的原創劇本，是你一字一句斟酌出來的故事，難道最後你連自己想寫的是什麼都不知道嗎？！", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果說痛苦才能孵化經典，現在不正是你應當走向創作巔峰的時刻嗎？", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拍攝即將結束的壓力，聽到即將拍攝天災的衝擊，兇手連環作案帶來的恐懼……什麼都有了！你還差什麼？", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“靈感之神”？哈哈！", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那只是你敷衍格蕾塔女士的說辭……你的神不會來的，你們已經失聯很久了！", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……誰啊……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "0,-60", "posto": "0,0"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……只要能讓我想出結尾，是誰都可以。", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#4$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}